        "content": "<p>The corresponding lemma in Mathlib is <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Probability/Independence/Basic.html#ProbabilityTheory.IndepFun_iff\">ProbabilityTheory.IndepFun_iff</a>. You should look at the code because the sigma-algebras are not explicit in the doc.</p>",
