    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Probability/Independence/Basic.html#ProbabilityTheory.indepFun_iff_measure_inter_preimage_eq_mul\">ProbabilityTheory.indepFun_iff_measure_inter_preimage_eq_mul</a> is a better match.</p>\n<p>The <code>MeasurableSpace</code> instance on Real is the Borel sigma-algebra, so to say that <code>B</code> is a Borel set you simply use <code>MeasurableSet B</code>.</p>",
